00089 template<unsigned DIM>
00090 MooneyRivlinMaterialLaw<DIM>::MooneyRivlinMaterialLaw(double c1, double c2)
00091     : mC1(c1),
00092       mC2(c2)
00093 {
00094     assert(DIM==2 || DIM ==3);
00095 
00096     // if dim==3, check that c2 was passed in, ie c2 isn't the default value
00097     if ((DIM==3) && (c2<MINUS_LARGE+1))
00098     {
00099         EXCEPTION("Two parameters needed for 3d Mooney-Rivlin");
00100     }
00101 
00102     if (c1 < 0.0)
00103     {
00104         EXCEPTION("c1 must be positive in mooney-rivlin"); // is this correct?
00105     }
00106 }
